                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable P</hi> 211.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's office—(read—Con<lb></lb>victed on the 5th Feb., 1th Vict., of larceny)—the prisoner is the person—he had six months.</p>
